OL,3,CFamily of ex footballer Kevin Campbell
OL,4,Cquestions treatment, inquest hears
OL,6,FAn inquest has heard that the the
OL,7,Ffamily of former footballer Kevin
OL,8,FCampbell has questioned why his heart
OL,9,Finfection was not identified months
OL,10,Fbefore his death.
OL,12,FThe former Everton and Arsenal
OL,13,Fstriker, who was 54, died at
OL,14,FManchester Royal Infirmary (MRI) on 15
OL,15,FJune 2024.
OL,17,FA provisional cause of death of multi-
OL,18,Forgan failure due to a heart infection
OL,19,F` infective endocarditis ` was given
OL,20,Fat the opening of his inquest the
OL,21,Ffollowing month.
