OL,6,FIt also emerged that Manchester
OL,7,FUniversity NHS Foundation Trust, which
OL,8,Fmanages the MRI, had declared a Level
OL,9,F5 patient safety incident ` the most
OL,10,Fserious category ` about aspects of
OL,11,Fhis care.
OL,13,FIt was said Mr Campbell had been fit
OL,14,Fand well until around January 2024
OL,15,Fwhen he had a number of stays in
OL,16,Fhospital before his final admission to
OL,17,Fthe MRI from May of that year.
