OL,6,FA pre-inquest review hearing on
OL,7,FWednesday, 26 February, was told he
OL,8,Fwas treated at the MRI for an initial
OL,9,Fsix-and-half weeks before his later
OL,10,Fadmission there, with a three-day stay
OL,11,Fat Salford Royal Hospital in between.
OL,13,FSebastian Naughton, the lawyer
OL,14,Frepresenting Mr Campbell's family,
OL,15,Fsaid the MRI's own investigation had
OL,16,Fidentified "some shortcomings" in
OL,17,Ftreatment, with reference to a delay
OL,18,Fin diagnosis during his final spell at
OL,19,Fthe MRI.
