OL,6,FHe said the family, who were not
OL,7,Fpresent at the hearing at Manchester
OL,8,FCoroner's Court, wanted to know more
OL,9,Fabout his earlier stay at the MRI.
OL,11,FHe said: "This is a medically complex
OL,12,Finquest. Kevin was admitted for six
OL,13,Fand half weeks to Manchester Royal
OL,14,FInfirmary in the earlier period.
OL,16,F"No clear underlying cause for heart
OL,17,Ffailure was identified in that period.
