OL,4,Cquestions treatment, inquest hears
OL,6,F"The family have questions about the
OL,7,Ffirst admission. In broad terms, how
OL,8,Fit was there was a six-and-a-half week
OL,9,Fadmission and no clear cause was
OL,10,Fidentified and whether there was an an
OL,11,Fearlier opportunity."
OL,13,FZak Golombek, who is the area coroner
OL,14,Ffor Manchester, adjourned proceedings
OL,15,Funtil a full inquest hearing which
OL,16,Fwill take place on a date which is yet
OL,17,Fto be fixed.
OL,19,FA spokesman for Manchester University
OL,20,FNHS Foundation Trust said it does not
OL,21,Fcomment on ongoing inquests.
