OL,4,Cquestions treatment, inquest hears
OL,6,FIn a long career Mr Campbell scored 59
OL,7,Fgoals in 224 games for Arsenal and,
OL,8,Falongside the 1990/91 league title, he
OL,9,Falso won the FA Cup, League Cup and
OL,10,FEuropean Cup Winners' Cup at Highbury.
OL,12,FHe spent three years at Nottingham
OL,13,FForest after joining them in 1995 and
OL,14,Fhad a one-season stop at Trabzonspor
OL,15,Fin Turkey before moving to Everton in
OL,16,F1999.
OL,18,FHe stayed at Everton until 2005, where
OL,19,Fhe spent time as captain under Walter
OL,20,FSmith, and ended his career with
OL,21,Fspells at West Brom and Cardiff.
